PEX2                     = 0.2108            $Variation of curvature Efx with load
PEX3                     = -1.5154           $Variation of curvature Efx with load squared
PEX4                     = -0.5              $Factor in curvature Efx while driving
PKX1                     = 33.6331           $Longitudinal slip stiffness Kfx/Fz at Fznom
PKX2                     = 0.00034021        $Variation of slip stiffness Kfx/Fz with load
PKX3                     = 0.3408            $Exponent in slip stiffness Kfx/Fz with load
